'''奈米龐克'''(Nanopunk)是指[[科幻小說|科幻小說]]的一個新興子流派，與其前輩類型[[賽博朋克|賽博朋克]]<ref>{{cite book |date=2014 |title=The Multiple Worlds of Fringe: Essays on the J.J. Abrams Science Fiction Series |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OdZuBAAAQBAJ&q=nanopunk+cyberpunk&pg=PA156 |location= |publisher= |page=156 |isbn=978-0-7864-7567-4 |access-date=20 May 2015 |last1=Cochran |first1=Tanya R. |last2=Ginn |first2=Sherry |last3=Zinder |first3=Paul |archive-date=2021-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211031010117/https://books.google.com/books?id=OdZuBAAAQBAJ&q=nanopunk+cyberpunk&pg=PA156 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="goonan">{{cite web |url=http://io9.com/345891/io9-talks-to-kathleen-ann-goonan-about-nanopunk-and-jazz |title=io9 Talks to Kathleen Ann Goonan About Nanopunk and Jazz |last1=Newitz |first1=Annalee |date=17 January 2008 |website= |publisher= |access-date=20 May 2015 |quote= |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402150432/http://io9.com/345891/io9-talks-to-kathleen-ann-goonan-about-nanopunk-and-jazz |dead-url=no }}</ref>及其某些其他[[賽博龐克衍生物|衍生物]]相比，仍處於起步階段。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.azonano.com/Details.asp?ArticleID=1918 |title=AZoNano - Nanopunk, Definition and Examples of Nanotechnology Based Nanopunk Speculative Science Fiction |date=Jun 12, 2007 |first= |last= |work=[[AZoNano|AZoNano]] |access-date=2020-10-17 |archive-date=2008-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080807055024/http://www.azonano.com/details.asp?ArticleID=1918 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

該類型與[[生物龐克|生物龐克]]特別相似，<ref name="nsf" />但描述了一個世界，其中廣泛使用[[奈米材料|奈米材料]]，而[[奈米技術|奈米技術]]是社會上主要的技術力量。

目前，這種類型主要關注奈米技術的藝術、心理<ref name="goonan" /> 和社會影響，而不是各個方面仍處於起步階段的奈米技術本身。與賽博龐克的特點不同，它具有堅韌不拔、低壽命但技術先進的特點，而賽博龐克則具有較黑暗的[[反烏托邦|反烏托邦]]特徵，它可以檢查奈米技術的潛在風險，以及更樂觀的觀點，可以強調奈米技術的潛在用途。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Huereca |first=Rafael Miranda |title=The evolution of cyberpunk into postcyberpunk - The role of cognitive cyberspaces, wetware networks and nanotechnology in science fiction |url=http://www.tdx.cat/bitstream/handle/10803/288302/rmh1de1.pdf |journal= |publisher= |volume= |issue= |pages= |doi= |access-date=19 May 2015 |archive-date=2016-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430093939/http://www.tdx.cat/bitstream/handle/10803/288302/rmh1de1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><!--(pros and cons of nanotech)--><ref name="nsf">{{cite web |url=http://bestsciencefictionbooks.com/nanopunk-science-fiction.php |title=Nanopunk Science Fiction |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |website= |publisher= |access-date= |quote= |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220220913/http://bestsciencefictionbooks.com/nanopunk-science-fiction.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>


